Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:22.75,正文,Principal,0,0,0,,有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:23.83,正文,Arata,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:27.58,supertext1,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,1)\frz305.8\pos(325.667,548.001)}要这个吗
